headline: Shell says head of downstream and renewables division Vigeveno to step down
summary: -Shell said on Thursday Huibert Vigeveno, its director of Downstream, Renewables and Energy Solutions will step down after 30 years with the energy major, and be replaced by insider Machteld de Haan....
